{"id": 2050, "genre": 1000, "title": "你属于哪种类型的滤镜选手？", "description": "你在晒图时代扮演着一个什么样的角色？", "record_count": 6818, "comment_count": 24, "praise_count": 0, "image": "img/paper/paper_show/20171205180624Cxo9Aj4FEuiaYlXK.jpg", "page_style": 0, "category": 1, "column": 2, "type": "paper", "date": "2017-12-06T17:00:00Z", "questions": [{"id": 3390, "title": "你属于哪种类型的滤镜选手？", "content": "你属于哪种类型的滤镜（照骗）选手？", "genre": 2, "options": [{"id": 252760, "content": "精致美化型，社交网络上的第二人格，当然要让自己变得更完美", "image": "img/option/option/20171205180908JXF5nEfa2Tdwrmzo.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 252761, "content": "娱乐欢脱型，摆鬼脸p自己或把朋友做成表情包，快乐至上", "image": "img/option/option/20171205181109tTIG2MXSlArWihwU.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 252762, "content": "探索实验型，随手拍张照都要试试不同滤镜的效果", "image": "img/option/option/20171205181407JXQwP320qcBF7AEt.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 252764, "content": "朴实无华型，不加滤镜不p照，保持网里如一，只留拍得好看的", "image": "img/option/option/20171205181531VmLrobQ71AaK0nhi.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 252765, "content": "生活升级型，给美食美景或小物加一层美化让生活看起来更有质感", "image": "img/option/option/20171205181706pfDlRs5VNCrjnaW2.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 252767, "content": "少女萌化型，给宠物、朋友或自己加一个少女心的滤镜添加爱意", "image": "img/option/option/20171205181836C6TxMU5gDEtZAmaq.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 252768, "content": "摄影工具型，每一张照片都是严肃的摄影作品，会调参数自制滤镜", "image": "img/option/option/201712051822231qJ6cb4zjIviGgKr.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}, {"id": 252769, "content": "事务需要型，职场恋爱或证件照上想让人留下个好印象", "image": "img/option/option/20171205182323lKENm62zpf3XQx1H.gif", "praise_count": 0, "perfect": 0, "select": 0}]}]}